&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an experienced and hard working HealthCare Assistant to join our dedicated Nursing team in Fletcher ward ( Care of the Elderly Ward) which is based on the Northwick Park site. You must be patient, enthusiastic, motivated with good communication skills, have the ability to work under pressure and most importantly passionate about elderly care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be expected to assist a team of Nurses and other healthcare professionals; the care and support that you offer patients during their time in hospital will be invaluable in ensuring that their time here is as comfortable and stress free as possible. Previous experience in an acute environment is desirable&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameJincy Mary JoseJob titleElderly Care Nurse PractitionerEmail addressjincyjose@nhs.netAdditional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please contact Junierose Gazzingan/ Jincy Jose on 07384900672 or 02088695070 to discuss about more details.&lt;/p&gt;
